en:
From 01/01 to 30/04 except January 1st and Easter Monday.
Closed Saturday and Sunday.
Monday : 8am to 12:30pm and 1:30pm to 5pm,
tuesday, wednesday and thursday : 8am to 12:30pm and 1:30pm to 6pm
friday: from 8 am to 1 pm and from 2 pm to 5 pm.

From 01/05 to 30/09
Open on Monday from 8am to 12:30pm and from 1:30pm to 5pm. Tuesday and Wednesday from 8am to 1pm and from 1:30pm to 6pm. Thursday from 8am to 12:30pm and from 1:30pm to 6pm. Friday from 8h30 to 12h30 and from 14h to 18h. Saturday from 9am to 12:30pm and from 2pm to 6pm. except on Ascension Thursday, Whit Monday, May 1st, May 8th, July 14th and August 15th.
Closed on Sundays.
Public holidays open :
-monday, May 1 Monday, May 8 Thursday, May 18, Monday, May 29, Friday, July 14 and Tuesday, August 15, 2023

saturday : 9am to 12:30pm and 2pm to 5pm.

From 01/10 to 31/12 except on public holidays.
Closed Saturday and Sunday.
From Monday to Thursday: from 8 am to 12:30 pm and from 1:30 pm to 6 pm and on Friday: from 8 am to 12:30 pm and from 2 pm to 5 pm.
